title: How To Talk to Yourself to Lose Weight
itunes:title: How To Talk to Yourself to Lose Weight
description:
Get the Free Course here:

http://phit.click/freecourse

 

Have you ever really listened to how you talk to yourself?

 

You know what I mean, that voice that says you're fat, you're ugly, or you're not good enough.

 

We all have that voice. Today I teach you how to hear that voice and decide whether or not you want to listen to it.
